Pi-STEP initiative Desktop / PiSi
Release: 0.1-alpha

==========================

### Pillars

- Operating System: Raspberry Pi OS Lite release (it is now Debian Bookworm 12). Not yet tested on Trixie.
- Window Manager: Window Maker 0.96.0 with PISI.themed and options: --no-dock  --no-clip --static. Some apps and tools are launched with the 'autostart' script of Wondow Maker.
- GNUstep has been built with Clang 19, ARC enabled and Grand Central Dispatch.
- Preferences Manager: SystemPreferences
- Workspace: GWorkspace and Recycler: 1.1.0 (02 2025) - Its own Desktop layer and its Dock (modern flavour) are shown. The Wallpaper is shown on this layer. It is a mandatory set to manage mounted removable devices on the Desktop and to unmount those by DND on the Recycler Icon.
- Theme: PISI (mostly inspired by Papirus Icon theme)
- Session: DBus
- Notifyer: dunst
- Compositing: compton
- Sys Infos: conky. Weather data is fetched from Wttr.in. The system monitoring is on: date, time, uptime, CPU, Memory, Storage and Networking.
- Alsa compliant Audio Mixer: see VolumeControl below.

===========================================

### Applications and Tools for the average user

- AddressManager (contacts)
- Cynthiune: Music Player
- GNUMail: Mail User Agent
- Grr: RSS Reader
- GSPdf: PS and PDF reader/viewer
- GWorkspace: the Workspace manager: see above.
- HelpViewer: .help reader.
- ImageViewer
- InnerSpace: screen saver
- Ink: Rich text (rtf and rtfd) editor.
- Librarian: Books and Documents Organizing
- MDFinder: within GWorkspace indexing
- OpenUp: archive manager
- Player: a wrapper for VLC video player
- Recycler: see GWorkspace.
- ScanImage: Scanner client
- ScreenShot: screen recorder
- SimpleAgenda: agenda
- SystemPreferences
- Terminal: a Terminal emulator
- TextEdit: text editor and note taking
- VolumeControl: AlsaMixer compliant mixer

### Wrappers

- Chromium.app: a wrapper for the chromium Web Browser
- EBookReader.app: a wrapper for FBReader
- Inkscape.app: guess...
- Writer.app: a wrapper for Focuswriter

### GNUstep Games

- Chess
- Freecell: a card game
- Gomoku: a TicTacToe game
- GShisen: a MahJong game
- LapisPuzzle: a Tetris like game

### Devel apps and tools

- EasyDiff: graphical Diff Tool
- Gemas: a specialized editor for objectiveC, plist...
- Gorm: Interface Builder for GNUstep
- ProjectCenter: Project Builder for GNUstep
- Thematic: a Theme Editor for GNUstep

### Extra GNUstep Applications list

- Calculator
- Cenon: Desktop Publishing 
- Dictionary: Dictionary Lookup for the English user
- FlexiSheet: a Spreadsheet inspired by Quantrix
- FontManager
- Graphos: a simple Vectorial Drawing app
- PikoPixel: Pixel Art
- PowerPaint: Bitmap Drawing
- PRICE: Image Manipulation program
- StepSync: Syncing Folders
